                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1208-18500610 t18500610-1208-punishment-164"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Russell Gurney, Esq.</hi>
               </p>
